error code: E0001
lang: fr
phase: parser
message: identifiant attendu
cause: The parser or lexer could not form the next valid source construct.
typical cases: nom manquant apres un mot-cle de declaration; liaison incomplete; chemin d'import tronque
step 1: Look at the highlighted token and complete or remove the construct around it.
correction: complete the syntax shape named by the parser label at the highlighted token
common pitfalls: n'ajoutez pas un nom factice qui ne correspond pas a la construction autour
fix: complete the syntax shape named by the parser label at the highlighted token
invalid example: proc () -> int { give 0 }
valid example: proc main() -> int { give 0 }
